<title>UK: BA extends cargo special deals for all April.</title>
<headline>BA extends cargo special deals for all April.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-03-14</dateline>
<text>
<p>British Airway's has again extended its special cutprice deals on air cargo rates and has published a new list of rates for the month of April, a BA Cargo spokesman said.</p>
<p>Under this latest extension BA's special promotion which started at the beginning of January apply to pallets and bin rates.</p>
<p>The latest package cover covers 17 North Atlantic, 3 South American, 14 southern region covering the Middle East, Africa and the Indian sub-continent, five Pacific and 13 European routes.</p>
<p>As with the March &quot;sale&quot; the special low rates must be booked within 72 hours of departure and cannot replace existing or permanent bookings and are subject to availability, the spokesman added.</p>
<p>As a wholesaling carrier the special deals are aimed at freight forwarders.</p>
